Dialogue: 0,0:00:01.39,0:00:07.20,Default,,0,0,0,,Astro Boy
Dialogue: 0,0:00:07.20,0:00:10.98,Default,,0,0,0,,Over the sky, la-la-la
Dialogue: 0,0:00:10.98,0:00:13.61,Default,,0,0,0,,Beyond the stars
Dialogue: 0,0:00:13.61,0:00:17.19,Default,,0,0,0,,Let's go, Atom
Dialogue: 0,0:00:17.19,0:00:21.02,Default,,0,0,0,,Until the jet limit
Dialogue: 0,0:00:21.02,0:00:24.99,Default,,0,0,0,,A heart-warming la-la-la
Dialogue: 0,0:00:24.99,0:00:27.56,Default,,0,0,0,,The child of science
Dialogue: 0,0:00:27.56,0:00:31.50,Default,,0,0,0,,It's a million-horsepower engine
Dialogue: 0,0:00:31.50,0:00:35.91,Default,,0,0,0,,Mighty Atom
Dialogue: 0,0:00:38.47,0:00:42.49,Default,,0,0,0,,Listen carefully, la-la-la
Dialogue: 0,0:00:42.49,0:00:45.14,Default,,0,0,0,,Open your eyes wide
Dialogue: 0,0:00:45.14,0:00:48.60,Default,,0,0,0,,That's right, Atom
Dialogue: 0,0:00:48.60,0:00:52.79,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't be off your guard
Dialogue: 0,0:00:52.79,0:00:56.50,Default,,0,0,0,,A righteous la-la-la
Dialogue: 0,0:00:56.50,0:00:59.14,Default,,0,0,0,,The child of science
Dialogue: 0,0:00:59.14,0:01:03.08,Default,,0,0,0,,It's a seven-force power
Dialogue: 0,0:01:03.08,0:01:07.33,Default,,0,0,0,,Mighty Atom
Dialogue: 0,0:01:27.45,0:01:29.66,Default,,0,0,0,,-Atom, be careful. -Okay!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:30.56,0:01:32.85,Default,,0,0,0,,How is it? Isn't it amazing?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:32.85,0:01:36.46,Default,,0,0,0,,With this, I'm going to watch the Rainbow Comet clearly.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:36.99,0:01:42.03,Default,,0,0,0,,Astronomy club students of Ochanomizu Elementary School for observing Rainbow Comet,
Dialogue: 0,0:01:42.03,0:01:44.21,Default,,0,0,0,,-Please go to gate seven. -Let's go!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:46.00,0:01:48.46,Default,,0,0,0,,-Be careful. -Good bye!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:49.42,0:01:50.16,Default,,0,0,0,,Atom.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:50.81,0:01:51.75,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:51.75,0:01:54.91,Default,,0,0,0,,At a time of need, you can communicate with me with this.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:54.91,0:01:55.41,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:55.84,0:01:58.07,Default,,0,0,0,,At a time of need?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:58.34,0:02:00.09,Default,,0,0,0,,Then, you mean...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:00.09,0:02:02.44,Default,,0,0,0,,No, as you all know,
Dialogue: 0,0:02:02.44,0:02:05.99,Default,,0,0,0,,today's activity is only for the kids' club on a holiday.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:05.99,0:02:10.93,Default,,0,0,0,,As an adviser, I need to be ready even for the smallest chance of...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:11.22,0:02:14.48,Default,,0,0,0,,A machine will only circumnavigate the course
Dialogue: 0,0:02:14.48,0:02:18.52,Default,,0,0,0,,calculated with computer, so it should be fine.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:18.52,0:02:23.46,Default,,0,0,0,,But Mrs. Shibukaki, is it really okay that a teacher doesn't accompany them?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:23.46,0:02:29.28,Default,,0,0,0,,My kid said that students should go by themselves for the sake of education.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:29.28,0:02:31.66,Default,,0,0,0,,They have grown up this much...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:36.58,0:02:40.31,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm late. Is everyone aboard already?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:40.31,0:02:44.17,Default,,0,0,0,,Are you worried, Mr. Beard? you don't have to worry.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:44.17,0:02:45.39,Default,,0,0,0,,But...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:45.84,0:02:48.31,Default,,0,0,0,,-It's all right. -Not that.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:04.74,0:03:07.54,Default,,0,0,0,,Good bye!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:13.93,0:03:18.26,Default,,0,0,0,,Atom vs. Atlas IV: The Menacing Comet
Dialogue: 0,0:03:24.22,0:03:26.46,Default,,0,0,0,,How beautiful the Earth is.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:27.35,0:03:29.82,Default,,0,0,0,,You are admiring at last?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:29.82,0:03:33.43,Default,,0,0,0,,I was on a space cruise ship last week as well.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:33.81,0:03:36.95,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm already tired of looking at the Earth from space.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:39.70,0:03:44.36,Default,,0,0,0,,-What? Shibukaki's eating already. -What do you care about when I eat my own food?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:44.36,0:03:45.71,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm going to eat, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:47.23,0:03:48.59,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll have instant noodles.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:49.53,0:03:53.16,Default,,0,0,0,,Space meals taste really bad.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:54.06,0:03:56.75,Default,,0,0,0,,Gosh! Meal time hasn't come yet!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:57.58,0:03:58.77,Default,,0,0,0,,Sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:59.39,0:04:01.85,Default,,0,0,0,,Even Doctor Ochanomizu said that you shouldn't
Dialogue: 0,0:04:01.85,0:04:04.00,Default,,0,0,0,,break the rules of Astronomy club!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:04.00,0:04:07.86,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes, because in space, a small fight can turn into a big accident!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:07.86,0:04:10.85,Default,,0,0,0,,Where is the proof that I ate already?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:10.85,0:04:12.97,Default,,0,0,0,,Look at Shibukaki.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:13.37,0:04:15.01,Default,,0,0,0,,Ha ha. Good for you.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:21.49,0:04:23.19,Default,,0,0,0,,Ah, it's a satellite.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:25.77,0:04:30.71,Default,,0,0,0,,That model was shot out in the 1900s. It's now expired.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:30.71,0:04:32.97,Default,,0,0,0,,But it's still orbiting.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:34.67,0:04:37.87,Default,,0,0,0,,Kenichi, isn't it time for you to study?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:37.87,0:04:41.13,Default,,0,0,0,,That's right. Everyone! Get back in your seat.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:41.42,0:04:42.51,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:48.43,0:04:51.39,Default,,0,0,0,,Everyone, before we arrive at comet and study,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:51.39,0:04:57.10,Default,,0,0,0,,let's practice putting on spacesuit, except for Atom, just in case.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:57.10,0:04:58.22,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:03.65,0:05:06.95,Default,,0,0,0,,-How do you close this? -Huh? There's no button.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:06.95,0:05:08.90,Default,,0,0,0,,That one is...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:09.16,0:05:11.62,Default,,0,0,0,,Ah! Mine wouldn't let my neck out!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:12.55,0:05:13.74,Default,,0,0,0,,Those are pants.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:14.16,0:05:17.26,Default,,0,0,0,,Are you done? Then, to become used to it,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:17.26,0:05:19.41,Default,,0,0,0,,let's study in spacesuits for a while.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:20.24,0:05:24.06,Default,,0,0,0,,A comet is a celestial body within the solar system.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:24.06,0:05:27.00,Default,,0,0,0,,It is made of frozen gas and small dust.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:27.00,0:05:29.17,Default,,0,0,0,,It wanders around space normally,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:29.17,0:05:32.31,Default,,0,0,0,,but it gets closer to the solar system, drawn by the Sun's gravitation.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:32.31,0:05:37.15,Default,,0,0,0,,And as its ice melts into gas by the Sun's light and heat, it falls.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:37.15,0:05:39.86,Default,,0,0,0,,That's called a tail of comet.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:39.86,0:05:43.24,Default,,0,0,0,,Rainbow Comet we will observe from now on
Dialogue: 0,0:05:43.24,0:05:47.24,Default,,0,0,0,,is famous for having a beautiful seven-colored tail.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:47.24,0:05:50.32,Default,,0,0,0,,Is Shibukaki listening well?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:52.16,0:05:57.97,Default,,0,0,0,,That gas shows colors because of that ice's ingredients.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:00.49,0:06:04.84,Default,,0,0,0,,Tamao, since it is controlled automatically, I told you not to go there...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:04.84,0:06:06.00,Default,,0,0,0,,It's all right, all right.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:10.07,0:06:11.63,Default,,0,0,0,,What is that sound?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:26.10,0:06:27.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Jump!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:27.42,0:06:28.78,Default,,0,0,0,,Was that you?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:31.65,0:06:35.08,Default,,0,0,0,,Ah, the noodles are running away. Stop! It's hot.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:35.08,0:06:37.87,Default,,0,0,0,,Gravitational stability device's switch is turned off!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:39.64,0:06:40.34,Default,,0,0,0,,What is this.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:42.67,0:06:44.38,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey! That.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:44.38,0:06:46.75,Default,,0,0,0,,It's my meat! Hey!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:46.75,0:06:50.42,Default,,0,0,0,,I won't let anyone take my food away.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:56.32,0:06:58.43,Default,,0,0,0,,Ah, soup...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:15.69,0:07:16.36,Default,,0,0,0,,No!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:28.62,0:07:29.96,Default,,0,0,0,,It hurts!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:40.93,0:07:43.92,Default,,0,0,0,,We are running on this smooth course.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:43.92,0:07:46.18,Default,,0,0,0,,That's nice.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:48.48,0:07:50.23,Default,,0,0,0,,I once wished to drink whiskey
Dialogue: 0,0:07:50.23,0:07:54.70,Default,,0,0,0,,as I take a spacewalk, even for only one time.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:54.70,0:07:59.54,Default,,0,0,0,,Didn't you say you wanted to go because you were worried about students?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:59.54,0:08:02.99,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, my worry as a teacher was of course the first reason.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:02.99,0:08:04.45,Default,,0,0,0,,About where are you now?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:04.45,0:08:08.79,Default,,0,0,0,,Their rocket will now approach the Moon soon.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:10.93,0:08:15.84,Default,,0,0,0,,Rainbow Comet is just approaching the Venus orbit.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:33.12,0:08:35.32,Default,,0,0,0,,Ah, it's Rainbow Comet.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:35.32,0:08:38.24,Default,,0,0,0,,-Huh? Where? -Which one is it?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:06.37,0:09:10.08,Default,,0,0,0,,It's beautiful as if space's jewels have been gathered together.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:10.08,0:09:11.41,Default,,0,0,0,,It's beautiful...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:12.73,0:09:14.90,Default,,0,0,0,,How beautiful...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:26.83,0:09:28.57,Default,,0,0,0,,What is it! What's up?!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:29.29,0:09:31.02,Default,,0,0,0,,What in the world happened?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:31.02,0:09:33.33,Default,,0,0,0,,The machine's working on its own!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:34.17,0:09:35.55,Default,,0,0,0,,Ah, it's a problem.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:39.72,0:09:41.60,Default,,0,0,0,,What's wrong, Atom?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:41.60,0:09:43.74,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't know.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:43.74,0:09:46.33,Default,,0,0,0,,It's certain that it is getting off the course.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:46.33,0:09:49.14,Default,,0,0,0,,What? Hurry and take it back!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:49.14,0:09:51.31,Default,,0,0,0,,Hand gear won't work, either.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:51.31,0:09:52.43,Default,,0,0,0,,For real?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:57.37,0:09:58.82,Default,,0,0,0,,Minister!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:58.82,0:10:01.38,Default,,0,0,0,,Ochanomizu Astronomy club's rocket is bit weird!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:01.38,0:10:02.28,Default,,0,0,0,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:12.09,0:10:13.18,Default,,0,0,0,,What is that?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:15.60,0:10:17.02,Default,,0,0,0,,Ah, that is...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:41.48,0:10:43.09,Default,,0,0,0,,It's gone.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:27.49,0:11:28.96,Default,,0,0,0,,It's been a long time, Atom.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:28.96,0:11:32.38,Default,,0,0,0,,That voice is from Atlas! Then this place is...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:32.38,0:11:34.30,Default,,0,0,0,,That's right. It's my castle.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:34.30,0:11:37.63,Default,,0,0,0,,It's the castle of the one who will soon become the ruler of the Earth.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:37.63,0:11:39.45,Default,,0,0,0,,You are still saying that?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:39.61,0:11:42.02,Default,,0,0,0,,What did you do to my friends?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:42.92,0:11:44.18,Default,,0,0,0,,I won't kill them.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:44.98,0:11:47.89,Default,,0,0,0,,Atom, do you now wish to follow what I say?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:47.89,0:11:50.89,Default,,0,0,0,,I told you I don't want to be involved in bad things!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:50.89,0:11:55.06,Default,,0,0,0,,Bad things? It would be bad only to humans.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:55.24,0:11:58.20,Default,,0,0,0,,But I want to be on good terms with humans.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:58.75,0:12:02.31,Default,,0,0,0,,How foolish. Human colleagues won't do any good.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:03.60,0:12:05.57,Default,,0,0,0,,Atom, let me show you something interesting.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:16.16,0:12:18.05,Default,,0,0,0,,Wow, it's a huge hat.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:20.21,0:12:23.94,Default,,0,0,0,,For who is it? Huh? I think I've seen it somewhere.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:24.75,0:12:27.64,Default,,0,0,0,,That's right! It looks exactly like mine. Someone...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:29.23,0:12:32.14,Default,,0,0,0,,-Atom! -Shibukaki, where are you?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:32.14,0:12:34.18,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm here.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:34.18,0:12:34.78,Default,,0,0,0,,Over there.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:41.16,0:12:42.31,Default,,0,0,0,,I heard a voice.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:42.31,0:12:43.65,Default,,0,0,0,,Shibukaki!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:00.06,0:13:02.34,Default,,0,0,0,,Everyone got super bigger.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:02.34,0:13:04.89,Default,,0,0,0,,And Shibukaki became smaller.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:04.89,0:13:06.69,Default,,0,0,0,,Ah! What is it!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:06.69,0:13:11.30,Default,,0,0,0,,Would you like to try? Now Shibukaki isn't scary anymore!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:11.43,0:13:15.39,Default,,0,0,0,,It looks like you've noticed. Good, let me show you more clearly.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:17.48,0:13:19.62,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't like it.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:31.59,0:13:33.03,Default,,0,0,0,,Ah, Tamao.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:35.28,0:13:40.51,Default,,0,0,0,,If you don't join my side, then I will make your friends into a piece of rice.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:40.51,0:13:42.54,Default,,0,0,0,,If you join my side, I'll return them to the Earth.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:42.54,0:13:44.18,Default,,0,0,0,,Now, what's your answer, Atom?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:58.12,0:14:00.16,Default,,0,0,0,,Atom. Atom!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:00.16,0:14:03.43,Default,,0,0,0,,Atom! There's no response here, either.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:04.20,0:14:08.27,Default,,0,0,0,,Tamao, you know what will happen if you become smaller, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:08.27,0:14:10.23,Default,,0,0,0,,Even if you ask like that...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:10.41,0:14:12.08,Default,,0,0,0,,You! Stop there!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:16.85,0:14:17.99,Default,,0,0,0,,Pervert!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:18.30,0:14:19.99,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm going to crush you!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:21.58,0:14:24.29,Default,,0,0,0,,-Help! -Help me!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:26.19,0:14:31.93,Default,,0,0,0,,Make them small! How dare a girl hits me!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:32.15,0:14:33.59,Default,,0,0,0,,They won't only get smaller.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:38.76,0:14:42.06,Default,,0,0,0,,After an hour like this, they will disappear from this world.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:47.37,0:14:51.87,Default,,0,0,0,,Atlas, stop it! I'll listen to what you say, so stop it!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:08.41,0:15:09.84,Default,,0,0,0,,Are you guys all right?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:14.66,0:15:16.53,Default,,0,0,0,,-Is everyone okay? -Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:26.40,0:15:27.53,Default,,0,0,0,,Put on your seat belt!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:27.53,0:15:29.95,Default,,0,0,0,,-Atom? Atom's not here. -Jump isn't, either.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:38.47,0:15:39.58,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh? What is it?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:39.58,0:15:42.70,Default,,0,0,0,,It's the Moon. But that's odd.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:42.88,0:15:45.17,Default,,0,0,0,,What's wrong? What is that?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:46.97,0:15:48.47,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, the rocket is!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:48.47,0:15:49.97,Default,,0,0,0,,What? They are safe?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:53.13,0:15:55.18,Default,,0,0,0,,But something's weird.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:55.59,0:15:59.87,Default,,0,0,0,,I calculated the distance between the course, and the rocket is right beside the Venus.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:00.38,0:16:01.11,Default,,0,0,0,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:01.94,0:16:03.85,Default,,0,0,0,,Wh, wh, what did you say?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:04.31,0:16:09.35,Default,,0,0,0,,Surface temperature of the Venus is 430℃. They are in trouble!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:19.06,0:16:23.45,Default,,0,0,0,,Atom! Atom! Atom!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:23.89,0:16:26.58,Default,,0,0,0,,Atom, you are finally my colleague.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:26.58,0:16:27.93,Default,,0,0,0,,Atom!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:31.29,0:16:33.71,Default,,0,0,0,,Atom! Atom!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:33.71,0:16:34.63,Default,,0,0,0,,Jump.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:34.92,0:16:36.26,Default,,0,0,0,,Atom!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:37.36,0:16:38.38,Default,,0,0,0,,Doctor!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:38.38,0:16:42.02,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, is it you, Atom? The rocket's headed to the Venus.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:42.44,0:16:44.40,Default,,0,0,0,,What? Venus?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:45.29,0:16:48.56,Default,,0,0,0,,You don't have to be surprised. If you use my castle,
Dialogue: 0,0:16:48.56,0:16:53.02,Default,,0,0,0,,you can freely move around even this vast space.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:53.66,0:16:56.95,Default,,0,0,0,,You were going to let this rocket be involved with the Venus from the beginning!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:57.69,0:17:01.74,Default,,0,0,0,,I just wanted to let you guys watch Rainbow Comet leisurely.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:04.37,0:17:05.70,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm going to save them!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:08.47,0:17:09.63,Default,,0,0,0,,Stop him!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:30.19,0:17:31.61,Default,,0,0,0,,Take it!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:32.69,0:17:33.88,Default,,0,0,0,,How is this?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:58.10,0:18:00.18,Default,,0,0,0,,Stop, Atom!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:00.18,0:18:03.49,Default,,0,0,0,,You made a great mistake to think that you can escape from me!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:05.95,0:18:08.35,Default,,0,0,0,,To where are we headed?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:10.02,0:18:11.31,Default,,0,0,0,,Ah, it's Atom.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:11.31,0:18:14.07,Default,,0,0,0,,-Atom! -Atom, help us!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:30.35,0:18:32.49,Default,,0,0,0,,-Here, supply energy. -Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:48.73,0:18:50.44,Default,,0,0,0,,There's no place to hide since we are in space.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:03.24,0:19:05.73,Default,,0,0,0,,Atom! What are you doing?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:10.71,0:19:12.13,Default,,0,0,0,,Ah! Zero-saver!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:27.39,0:19:32.18,Default,,0,0,0,,Atom, I won't make pranks anymore. Please don't use the ice!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:44.71,0:19:46.12,Default,,0,0,0,,If you are going to keep insisting on escaping...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:08.94,0:20:09.76,Default,,0,0,0,,That's right!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:18.77,0:20:19.53,Default,,0,0,0,,How's this?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:27.34,0:20:28.35,Default,,0,0,0,,Atom.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:37.37,0:20:39.42,Default,,0,0,0,,Look at what zero-saver can do!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:53.75,0:20:55.28,Default,,0,0,0,,Ah, Atom's gone.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:48.71,0:21:51.80,Default,,0,0,0,,Why would you reject me so much?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:52.16,0:21:55.03,Default,,0,0,0,,Good, Atom! Then, keep in mind
Dialogue: 0,0:21:55.03,0:21:57.45,Default,,0,0,0,,that you are the enemy of me, Atlas, from now on!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:29.44,0:22:31.78,Default,,0,0,0,,Atom balloon in sky.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:31.78,0:22:36.00,Default,,0,0,0,,But it's a scary bomb that attacks children.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:36.00,0:22:38.84,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh? I'm not the culprit.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:38.84,0:22:42.05,Default,,0,0,0,,Gosh! How can they do that to Uran as well?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:42.05,0:22:45.44,Default,,0,0,0,,All right. I'm going to find the real culprit.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:45.44,0:22:48.21,Default,,0,0,0,,Balloon bomb, I'm coming for you!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:51.30,0:22:55.06,Default,,0,0,0,,Next on Astro Boy, "The Devil's Balloon." Look forward to it!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:55.06,0:22:56.30,Default,,0,0,0,,Next on Astro Boy "The Devil's Balloon"
Dialogue: 0,0:23:06.36,0:23:10.37,Default,,0,0,0,,My arms and legs
Dialogue: 0,0:23:10.37,0:23:13.89,Default,,0,0,0,,fly over the sky with a jet
Dialogue: 0,0:23:13.89,0:23:18.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Astro Boy
Dialogue: 0,0:23:18.00,0:23:20.76,Default,,0,0,0,,Mighty Atom
Dialogue: 0,0:23:20.76,0:23:24.71,Default,,0,0,0,,Inside my waist,
Dialogue: 0,0:23:24.71,0:23:28.23,Default,,0,0,0,,a machine gun's light
Dialogue: 0,0:23:28.23,0:23:32.35,Default,,0,0,0,,Astro Boy
Dialogue: 0,0:23:32.35,0:23:35.51,Default,,0,0,0,,Mighty Atom
Dialogue: 0,0:23:35.51,0:23:39.19,Default,,0,0,0,,Searchlight's eyes
Dialogue: 0,0:23:39.19,0:23:42.76,Default,,0,0,0,,Laser Blast's hands
Dialogue: 0,0:23:42.76,0:23:49.98,Default,,0,0,0,,Seven powers, Wa Wa Wa Wa
Dialogue: 0,0:23:49.98,0:23:56.24,Default,,0,0,0,,We fight for the peace
Dialogue: 0,0:23:56.24,0:24:03.46,Default,,0,0,0,,Come on, let's go together
